<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَوَقُودُهَا الشَّهَوَاتُ وَالْحَسَرَاتُ وَالآ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>لامُ لا تَخْبُو مَدَى الأَزْمَانِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَبْدَانُهُمْ أَجْدَاثُ هَاتِيكَ النُّفُو<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>سِ اللائِي قَدْ قُبِرتْ مَعَ الأَبْدَانِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَرْوَاحُهُمْ فِي وَحْشَةٍ وَجُسُومُهُمْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فِي كَدْحِهَا لا فِي رِضَا الرَّحْمَنِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>هَرَبُوا مِن الرِّقِ الَّذِي خُلِقُوا لَهُ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَبُلُو بِرِقِّ النَّفْسِ وَالشَّيْطَانِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>لا تَرْضَ مَا اخْتَارُوا هُمُ لِنُفُوسِهِمْ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فَقَدْ ارْتَضُوا بِالذُّلِّ وَالْحِرْمَانِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>لَوْ سَاوَتْ الدُّنْيَا جَنَاحَ بَعُوضَةٍ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>لَمْ َيَسْقِ مِنْهَا الرَّبُّ ذُو الْكُفْرَانِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>لَكِنَّهَا وَاللهِ أَحْقَرُ عِنْدَهُ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>مِنْ ذَا الْجَنَاحِ الْقَاصِرِ الطَّيَرَانِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَلَقَدْ تَوَلَّتْ بَعْدُ عَنْ أَصْحَابِهَا<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فَالسَّعْدُ مِنْهَا حَلَّ بِالدَّبَرَانِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>لا يُرْتَجَى مِنْهَا الْوَفَاءُ لِصَبِّهَا<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>أَيْنَ الْوَفَا مِنْ غَادِرِ خَوَّانِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>طُبِعَتْ عَلَى كَدْرِ فَكَيْفَ يَنَالُهَا<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>صَفْوٌ أهَذَا قَطُ فِي إِمْكَانِ ... &gt;?<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>